<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Media Object</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container py-4">
        <h1 class="mb-4">Media Object Layout</h1>
        
        <div class="d-flex mb-4">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/64" class="flex-shrink-0 me-3 rounded" alt="...">
            <div>
                <h5 class="mt-0">Media heading</h5>
                <p>This is some content from a media component. You can replace this with any content and adjust it as needed.</p>
                <p>Donec sed odio dui. Nullam quis risus eget urna mollis ornare vel eu leo. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="d-flex mb-4">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/64" class="flex-shrink-0 me-3 rounded-circle" alt="...">
            <div>
                <h5 class="mt-0">Media heading</h5>
                <p>This is some content from a media component. You can replace this with any content and adjust it as needed.</p>
                
                <!-- Nested media object -->
                <div class="d-flex mt-3">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/64" class="flex-shrink-0 me-3 rounded-circle" alt="...">
                    <div>
                        <h5 class="mt-0">Nested media</h5>
                        <p>This is nested media object content.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="d-flex">
            <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/64" class="flex-shrink-0 me-3 align-self-center" alt="...">
            <div>
                <h5 class="mt-0">Center-aligned media</h5>
                <p>This is some content from a media component. The image is vertically centered.</p>
                <p class="mb-0">Donec sed odio dui. Nullam quis risus eget urna mollis ornare vel eu leo. Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
